label: Book of hours (Dutch), LTK 298

metadata.label: Content
metadata.value: Contains, in Dutch: (ff. 1r-12v). Calendar for the diocese of Utrecht. - (ff. 13r-41v) Hours of the Virgin. Incomplete (begin and last lines missing). - (ff. 42r-58v) Long Hours of the Cross. Incomplete (begin missing) - (ff. 59r-78r) Hours of the Holy Spirit. - (ff. 79r-95v) Hours of Eternal Wisdom. - (ff. Penitential Psalms and Litany of Saints. Incomplete (begin missing). - (ff. 109r-137v) Office of the Dead. - Empty: ff. 78v, 108v, three uncounted leaves a-c between ff. 12 and 13.

metadata.label: Note
value: Several opening leaves of major texts were cut out: after ff. 13, 41, 95.
Origin: Based on the decoration, possibly produced by the Domus Parva in Zwolle (See Wierda 1995)
Also described by MMDC and A.W. Byvanckgenootschap (database RKD, The Hague).
